results.title: Color Theory
results.description:
This month, we’re drawing inspiration from the refined colors of Surface devices. Making statements in ice blue, poppy red, sandstone, platinum, and black - this opaque palette feels both nostalgic and futuristic. Whether it’s a piece of furniture, clothing, architectural feature or texture - capture any of these hues in the wild and share them for a chance to be featured.

Check out the color palette here
